        Provides the standard interface for calling the trafficData2 MATLAB function with 3 comma-separated input arguments. Input arguments may be passed as sub-classes of com.mathworks.toolbox.javabuilder.MWArray, or as arrays of any supported Java type. Arguments passed as Java types are converted to MATLAB arrays according to default conversion rules.

        Description as provided by the author of the MATLAB function: 

         
 % 寮版规

        nargout - Number of outputs to return.
        rhs - The inputs to the MATLAB function.
        返回:
